                    "text": "pick you up",
                    "colorize": true
                },
                {
                    "text": " at 7 p.m. — just be waiting outside your apartment building"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Separable phrasal verb: 'pick me up' or 'pick up my friend'. NOT the same as 'pick up' meaning 'lift physically' or 'learn casually' (different contexts)."
        },
        {
